Package: bzip2
Version: 1.0.1
Revision: 1
Essential: yes
Depends: stow
Source: ftp://sourceware.cygnus.com/pub/bzip2/v100/bzip2-1.0.1.tar.gz
CompileScript: patch -p1 <%p/fink/patch/bzip2-1.0.1-1.patch
 make
InstallScript: make install PREFIX=%i
