CommentPort: Doesn't use autoconf, but comes with a useful Makefile.
 It's hardwired for gcc, though. Mac OS X PB uses a gcc-based
 compiler, but it's installed as "cc", not "gcc". The patch changes
 the Makefile to use "cc".
 .
 The shared library is not built right now.
